    <string name="changelog_content">📦 v1.2.0 (2025-04-05)

✨ New Features:
• Check-in task system with custom task lists &amp; reminder times
• Batch alarm generation (add or replace existing alarms)
• Battery optimization guide for reliable alarms
• Brand-specific setup guides (Xiaomi, Huawei, OPPO, vivo)

🔧 Improvements:
• Fixed alarm timing calculation (no more 20-min delay)
• Settings page redesigned with alarm reliability section
• New "Check-in" tab in bottom nav

---

📦 v1.1.0 (2025-04-04)

• Custom recording path
• Duplicate offset settings (hour/minute)
• WiFi sync for LAN data transfer
• 24-hour chime (TTS voice / musical bell)
• Multiple TTS engine &amp; voice selection

---

📦 v1.0.0 (2025-04-01)

• Core alarm functionality (create, edit, delete, group)
• Drag-and-drop group sorting
• Custom ringtones (system + local recordings)
• Vibration toggle
• Theme switching (dark / forest / sunset)
• Chinese &amp; English bilingual support
• Data export/import backup (JSON + audio files)</string>
